Class RouteManager.TravelTimeOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.RouteManager.TravelTimeOptions
  • Enclosing class:
    RouteManager

    public static class RouteManager.TravelTimeOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing the Travel Time Request Options for the server. The mandatory parameters are the route ID, travel time count and travel time interval. Optional Parameters are Departure time - defaults to NOW Arrival Time - ignored if the departure time is specified.
